===Cardinal number===
'''quadrillion'''

# (''US; modern British & Australian, [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]]'') A [[thousand]] [[trillion]]: 1 followed by fifteen zeros, 10<sup>15</sup>.
# (''dated British & Australian, [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]]'') A [[million]] [[trillion]]: 1 followed by twenty-four zeros, 10<sup>24</sup>.

* ''Western (Arabic) Numeral'' '''quadrillion''', '''10<sup>15</sup>''' [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]], '''10<sup>24</sup>''' [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]]
** Previous: [[trillion]]: [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]] 10<sup>12</sup>, [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]] 10<sup>18</sup>
** Next: [[quintillion]]: [[w:Long and short scales|short scale]] 10<sup>18</sup>, [[w:Long and short scales|long scale]] 10<sup>30</sup>
* ISO prefix: [[peta-]] ([[w:Long and short scales|short scale]]), [[yotta-]] ([[w:Long and short scales|long scale]]).

